"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934590-olympics-2024-Gianmarco-Tamberi-high-jump\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Gianmarco Tamberi might've been taken to hospital earlier today, but the Italian still turned out for the men's high jump final at the2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gianmarco Tamberi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 82, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9993130327528364, \"rank\": 0.000649580172696734, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi had posted onInstagrama snap of him inside an ambulance, with reports he'd been suffering from abdominal pain.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement shared to his social media, Tamberi said: \\\"It's been 10 hours and the kidney colic is still not over.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pain I have been feeling this morning, no matter how strong, is nothing compared to what I am feeling inside.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even what was my last certainty is about to fade away..... Just been rushed to the ER after vomiting blood twice.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"score\": 0.999993748225722, \"rank\": 6.251802611816195e-06, \"text\": \"ER\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now I am going to have more tests to see what's going on, I will update you because the many messages I am getting and the love you are showing me, the less I deserve a response.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything I have dreamed for this day except living such a nightmare...\\\"  Despite the pain, the high jumper who took gold in Tokyo turned out for the final at the Stade de France in Paris.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9446006805686273, \"rank\": 0.0586157169295703, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997589839, \"rank\": 2.411195819973505e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 32-year-old had snatched the headlines three years earlier when he and Qatari high-jumper Mutaz Barshim went viral for sharing the gold medal at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mutaz_Essa_Barshim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mutaz Barshim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mutaz_Essa_Barshim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mutaz_Essa_Barshim\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Olympic cyclist accused of 'deliberately headbutting' Team GB star in crash  Hell of a day for Italy's Gianmarco Tamberi so far.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7438837882748522, \"rank\": 0.325319508221363, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999998550242813, \"rank\": 1.4480799702075058e-07, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gianmarco Tamberi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gianmarco_Tamberi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was taken to hospital this morning but is still here competing in the men's high jump.Looks in pain.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just cleared 2.22 on his third attempt.pic.twitter.com/xJq3bCE3iU    But it wasn't the medal-laden evening Tamberi had hoped for this time around, with the athlete crashing out of the high jump competition early on.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi had cleared the initial 2.22 meter barrier but was forced to bow out at 2.27 metres, having posted three failed attempts.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was unable to keep his emotions in check following his departure from the competition, with a frustrated Tamberi having to be consoled by his coaching team.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Burying his head into the chest of the Italian delegates, a teary Tamberi struggled to cope with the situation, but the Stade de France crowd were quick to give him 